cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

The paper deals with using Recurrent Neural Networks as a postfilter for speech synthesis, which involves both speech processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves training the postfilter using a novel approach, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
